'''Marwan Marzouk Boodai''' is a [[Kuwait]]i businessman and currently the CEO of Boodai Group, and chairman of [[Jazeera Airways]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=25890085&ticker=JAZEERA:KK&previousCapId=24053440&previousTitle=JAZEERA%20AIRWAYS|title=Marwan Marzouk Boodai|publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek|accessdate=8 December 2010}}</ref>
The Boodai Group runs many businesses in Kuwait such as Jazeera Airways, City Bus, City Taxi, Limousine Services etc.<ref>[http://www.4-traders.com/business-leaders/Marwan-Boodai-072Q0R-E/biography/ Marwan Marzouk Jassim Boodai]</ref><ref>[http://gulfbusiness.com/lists/top-100-powerful-arabs-2014/marwan-marzouk-boodai/ Marwan Marzouk Boodai]</ref>

