'''Siri Fürst''' (born 1958) is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] businessperson.

She was a partner in the Considium Consulting Group. Educated at the [[Norwegian School of Economics and Business Administration]], she worked in [[Hafslund]], [[Hafslund Nycomed]] and [[Nycomed Pharma]] from 1984 to 1999 and as managing director of [[DiaGenic]] from 1999 to 2003.<ref name=aker>{{cite web |url=http://www.akersolutions.com/Internet/AboutUs/Board+and+Executive+Management/Boardmembers.htm|title=Board members|author=[[Aker Solutions]]|accessdate=2008-11-07}}</ref>

She is a member of the board of [[Aker Solutions]].<ref name=aker/>

